{"tid":2301800,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我有嘢想同你講","createTime":"2020-11-26T14:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T17:11:56.000Z","uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea28252468f1600f8bcfe725aedf7a0f8f34ea3","tid":2301800,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"好大風，頭先瞓唔着嗰陣時諗起你，發夢又諗起你，冇同你傾偈三日，每秒都有諗起你，我真係未試過咁鍾意一個人，我份人好容易放棄的，但係今次一啲放棄嘅心都冇。<br />\n<br />\n曾經有一段真摯的愛情擺喺我眼前，我冇去珍惜，等到失去左先至後悔莫及，塵世間最痛苦嘅事莫過於此，如果上天能夠比我一個重新嚟過嘅機會，我希望可以對嗰個女仔講：「我愛你」，如果一定要為呢段愛加一個期限的話，我希望係...... 一萬年。<br />\n<br />\n可能咁樣講好on9，但係，呢個係我而家嘅諗法，我好想比幸福你。"},{"pid":"ffc5a3fbc7a90d61aacfd8a3b3aab97884997d01","tid":2301800,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"佛理？"},{"pid":"b121528a60211f26719b5eb140fb88dbb8f4bfb7","tid":2301800,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffc5a3fbc7a90d61aacfd8a3b3aab97884997d01","tid":2301800,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"佛理？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"Crossover左兩段有感情的文字"},{"pid":"eda6a235158624c037dbc33eef8ad136eec43e0c","tid":2301800,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd93292cd4559c8b4168b811c990be5b460cf0f","tid":2301800,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eda6a235158624c037dbc33eef8ad136eec43e0c","tid":2301800,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"有創意？"},{"pid":"666e5e5f34c9a91cb918c22da29424d905245e8f","tid":2301800,"uid":38338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"ok 收到"},{"pid":"303b638eb36d217d9d16f6f2